WEBVTT


1
00:00:00.966 --> 00:00:01.933
Zi Han

2
00:00:02.233 --> 00:00:03.966
It's all my fault, my child

3
00:00:14.933 --> 00:00:15.833
I'm sorry

4
00:00:15.833 --> 00:00:17.066
The surgery failed

5
00:00:17.066 --> 00:00:18.000
We did our best

6
00:00:19.766 --> 00:00:20.933
Couldn't even take care of a child

7
00:00:20.933 --> 00:00:21.866
Is this what being a mother is?

8
00:00:22.500 --> 00:00:23.466
If you don't want to live, just die

9
00:00:23.466 --> 00:00:24.366
No one will stop you

10
00:00:24.366 --> 00:00:26.333
A fat woman who always embarrasses me

11
00:00:26.333 --> 00:00:27.633
Useless

12
00:00:27.933 --> 00:00:29.166
Can't even give birth to a son

13
00:00:29.166 --> 00:00:30.533
And you caused the death of our daughter

14
00:00:30.933 --> 00:00:33.066
Why weren't you the one who died?

15
00:00:33.066 --> 00:00:35.233
Auntie, don't be angry,

16
00:00:35.233 --> 00:00:36.833
Sister Dao Dao is already heartbroken

17
00:00:36.866 --> 00:00:38.366
If it were me,

18
00:00:38.433 --> 00:00:39.933
I would have died long ago

19
00:00:41.433 --> 00:00:42.733
Zi Han

20
00:00:43.700 --> 00:00:45.333
Mother is coming to be with you

21
00:00:48.533 --> 00:00:49.300
Wen Xu,

22
00:00:49.300 --> 00:00:50.466
don't be angry anymore

23
00:00:50.500 --> 00:00:51.900
If that fat woman finds out

24
00:00:51.900 --> 00:00:53.466
that her daughter's death is related to us

25
00:00:53.466 --> 00:00:54.966
will I still be able to get her shares?

26
00:00:57.266 --> 00:00:58.000
Alright,

27
00:00:58.266 --> 00:00:59.900
instead of talking about this, think carefully

28
00:00:59.900 --> 00:01:02.100
about how to get those shares

29
00:01:02.366 --> 00:01:04.400
You have to live with her every day

30
00:01:04.400 --> 00:01:06.533
it feels like torture

31
00:01:07.300 --> 00:01:08.366
Tell me,

32
00:01:08.366 --> 00:01:09.833
if she dies

33
00:01:10.566 --> 00:01:13.100
won't all those shares be mine?

34
00:01:21.066 --> 00:01:21.733
So...

35
00:01:23.266 --> 00:01:26.100
You married me for the company

36
00:01:26.400 --> 00:01:29.266
You're the ones who killed Zi Han

37
00:01:29.500 --> 00:01:32.433
She was your biological daughter

38
00:01:32.433 --> 00:01:33.400
Jian Dao,

39
00:01:33.400 --> 00:01:34.600
since things have come to this

40
00:01:34.600 --> 00:01:35.600
I don't want to hide it anymore

41
00:01:36.166 --> 00:01:37.833
All these years with you

42
00:01:38.300 --> 00:01:40.100
were just to take over Jian An Real Estate

43
00:01:41.133 --> 00:01:43.500
Have you ever looked at yourself in the mirror?

44
00:01:43.800 --> 00:01:44.900
You're fat

45
00:01:44.900 --> 00:01:46.500
Do you think I want to be with you?

46
00:01:46.500 --> 00:01:48.333
Look at yourself in the mirror

47
00:01:48.333 --> 00:01:49.300
You're all fat

48
00:01:49.300 --> 00:01:51.000
Seeing you makes me sick

49
00:01:56.733 --> 00:01:57.766
Xiang Wen Xu,

50
00:01:59.100 --> 00:02:00.800
I became like this

51
00:02:00.800 --> 00:02:02.466
because I gave birth to your child

52
00:02:02.466 --> 00:02:04.600
How dare you criticize me!

53
00:02:05.166 --> 00:02:05.966
Jian Dao, Jian Dao,

54
00:02:06.800 --> 00:02:08.366
I don't want to pretend anymore

55
00:02:10.566 --> 00:02:11.633
As long as you die

56
00:02:11.833 --> 00:02:14.266
Jian An Real Estate will naturally be mine

57
00:02:18.100 --> 00:02:18.866
Don't run

58
00:02:21.800 --> 00:02:22.500
Stop!

59
00:02:27.166 --> 00:02:28.733
Pretending to be a good husband all these years,

60
00:02:28.733 --> 00:02:29.566
I'm exhausted

61
00:02:30.700 --> 00:02:31.500
If I had known it would be this troublesome

62
00:02:31.500 --> 00:02:33.266
I should have killed you sooner

63
00:02:33.933 --> 00:02:35.633
Don't come near me

64
00:02:37.366 --> 00:02:38.166
Let me go!

65
00:02:39.666 --> 00:02:40.733
Die

66
00:02:40.733 --> 00:02:42.133
Your death would be good for everyone
